KnowledgeBase.Title: Example Structure compareNE 003
KnowledgeBase.RelatedFunctions: compare compareEQ compareLE compareGE compareLT compareGT

Example.Description: These examples use the compareNE function to compare two Structures and return the Boolean value, true or false. The corresponding keys and values of each Structure are compared to determine whether one Structure is equal to the other.

Syntax.Note: The first Structure is lesser than the second Structure.
